{"tid":1420913,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"闊過樹窿——盡訴心中情[公海] 再post","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T07:01:50.000Z","uid":244876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"622428a02516574d7b4a3ac4264e653dcf0336b5","tid":1420913,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，有人同伴侶分手，有人晚晚夜歸，有人洗到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n<br />\n例子如下(1):<br />\n琴日老豆同老母嘈<br />\n佢地兩個政治立場差好遠<br />\n我好攰，想講但係有心無力 好多日唔夠訓<br />\n工都搞到冇精神返 想死<br />\n<br />\n(2):<br />\n返工好攰 日日被上面老點<br />\n頂住好大壓力 又想請假又唔批<br />\n日日OT O到飲幾百杯咖啡 去廁所都成浸咖啡味<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OY6xwlZRBnmlPaCATObKog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOY6xwlZRBnmlPaCATObKog&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=9991f71f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OY6xwlZRBnmlPaCATObKog</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />post錯地方會錯意好似"},{"pid":"5a1d99aa09eb6a5b2bcc6e4e7d23349770ed95da","tid":1420913,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:21:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cebb017f31682f3c2235a7543ddd09fe0f443b31","tid":1420913,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0db0a9928cd28637f7fab86dffce8324a34589b4","tid":1420913,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:32:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb68e508fed6591724c2d72677e8d511553be4db","tid":1420913,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:01:50.000Z","msg":"push"}]}